            <title>[HBASE-3791] Display total number of zookeeper connections on master.jsp</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3791</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Quite often, user needs to telnet to Zookeeper and type &apos;stats&apos; to get the connections, or count the connections on zk.jsp&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should display the total number of connections beside the link to zk.jsp on master.jsp&lt;/p&gt;</description>
